Package com.nookure.staff.api.item

Class StaffItem

java.lang.Object
com.nookure.staff.api.item.StaffItem
public abstract class StaffItem extends Object
Represents a staff item that can be added to the user's inventory. this staff item does not have any functionality until it implements an interface that represents a staff action.
